Embedded third-party source code
--------------------------------

`data/glm52_import/normalized/calib_prompts.jsonl` is a frozen historical
record of the calibration/import set actually used at build time. 87 of its
1,536 rows are SWE-bench-style agent trajectories whose `/testbed/` context
embeds verbatim source-code excerpts from the following open-source
projects (row content is unmodified — editing it would falsify the record
of what calibration consumed):

    astroid, dvc, faker, feedparser, glom, monai, oauthlib, pandas,
    paramiko, starlette, strsimpy

